OL,5, The wife of a man who took his own life
OL,6, at a mental health unit after a doctor 
OL,7, thought he was feigning symptoms has   
OL,8, described his care as "shocking".      
OL,10,FGary Mavin was an inpatient for three  
OL,11,Fweeks at the Priory Hospital in Arnold,
OL,12,FNottinghamshire, in August 2020.       
OL,14,FA coroner found "inexplicable failings"
OL,15,Fby the hospital and called it "one of  
OL,16,Fthe worst examples of care provided to 
OL,17,Fa vulnerable patient".                 
OL,19,FThe Priory said there had been many    
OL,20,Fchanges since Mr Mavin's death.        
